WEBVTT

00:00:13.629 --> 00:00:16.284
Today, we're going to look at the world of Rome

00:00:16.284 --> 00:00:18.334
through the eyes of a young girl.

00:00:18.334 --> 00:00:20.920
Here she is, drawing a picture of herself

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:24.505
in the atrium of her father's enormous house.

00:00:24.505 --> 00:00:26.421
Her name is Domitia,

00:00:26.421 --> 00:00:29.051
and she is just 5 years old.

00:00:29.051 --> 00:00:31.405
She has an older brother who is fourteen,